#lg C	barsud


@(13-16=c2521.C.13) Warrior with head held high, respected lord, son who rises up to protect his father, @wDN{Nergal}, angry sea, inspiring fearsome terror, whom no one knows how to confront, youth whose advance is a hurricane and a flood battering the lands, @wDN{Nergal}, dragon covered with gore, drinking the blood of living creatures!

