#lg F	barsud


@(30-35=c2521.F.30) Shepherd who organises, giving just verdicts like the noble youth @wDN{Utu}! @wDN{Nergal}, pile up his malefactors in heaps for him, for @wRN{Šu-ilīšu}, the prince who displays lasting divine powers among the @wDN{Anuna} gods! May @wRN{Šu-ilīšu} rely on you, may he be made joyful by you! May he walk as the shepherd whose name is extolled among this people like that of @wDN{Utu}! May all lands and the teeming people bless (?) the life of @wRN{Šu-ilīšu}!

#trailer rubric	barsud


@(36=c2521.F.36) @fsux{Barsud}.

