#lg H	sa-jara


@(39-53=c2521.H.39) Lord of the underworld, who acts swiftly in everything, whose terrifying anger smites the wicked, @wDN{Nergal}, single-handed crusher, who tortures the disobedient -- the powerful ones, fearsome terror of the Land, respected lord and hero, established offspring of @wDN{Nunamnir} ……! @wDN{Nergal}, who sprinkles cool water on the angry heart of @wDN{Enlil}, great lord ……! @wDN{Nergal}, standing ready for battle, superior with head lifted high, lord who overpowers all the wicked like a lion, ……, unwilling to turn back at the door-pivot! @wDN{Nergal}, great battle-net for malefactors, covering all enemies! Warrior, you are a great and furious storm upon the land which disobeys your father! @wDN{Nergal}, you terrify the walled cities and the settlements as you stand in your path like a wild bull, smiting them with your great horns! @wDN{Nergal}, you have consumed their brickwork as if it were chaff in the air. When you lift your furious face, no one dare look at it. When you have …… 
{in the Land
} 
{@noteanchor{1 ms. has instead:} among that people
} , @wDN{Nergal}, you pour their blood down the wadis like rain. You afflict all the wicked peoples with woe, and deprive all of them of their lives.


@(54-62=c2521.H.54) Youthful @wDN{Nergal}, those who are saved with your help magnify you with praise! Lord, you have avenged @wDN{Enlil}! He has calmed the heart of his father! @wDN{Nergal} the strong, son who subdues the foreign lands for @wDN{Nunamnir}: may you assist in battle, furious fight and combat the shepherd whom @wDN{An} has chosen among the numerous people, the good and exalted youth of the Great Mountain @noteref{= @wDN{Enlil}} -- @wRN{Šu-ilīšu}, who publicly performs the purification rites, born of @wDN{Ninlil}! @wDN{Nergal}, catch his malefactors for him like swallows! You cover the land which is disobedient to him with a raging storm; may you be the weapon of slaughter! Heap up in piles for @wRN{Šu-ilīšu} the inhabitants of the city that does not support him.

